   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued September 20 at 1:37PM EDT until September 22 at 2:00PM EDT by NWS Newport/Morehead City NC</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas
4 to 6 ft expected.

* WHERE...The coastal waters from Duck to Oregon Inlet.

* WHEN...From 4 AM Sunday to 2 PM EDT Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
